Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.05,0:00:58.63,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}My Silky Love 24時間ずっと
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.63,0:01:02.17,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}My Silky Love キミのこと想うたび
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.17,0:01:05.70,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}My Silky Love もどかしいこの気持ち
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.70,0:01:09.71,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}My Silky Love ただ溢れかえってく
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.11,0:01:13.59,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}スキと言えば簡単なのに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.67,0:01:16.97,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}キミが前に来ちゃうと
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.24,0:01:23.38,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}個性がそびえ　私のコトを邪魔してる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.35,0:01:27.78,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}いつもならば強気でイケる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.78,0:01:31.29,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}そんな性格なのに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.48,0:01:37.46,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}どんな頑張ってみても壁は崩せない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.57,0:01:41.19,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}察して欲しい…　この気持ちを
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.19,0:01:44.76,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}だから私は　いつもキミに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.76,0:01:48.41,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}大好きだよと　送る視線
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.51,0:01:52.16,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}最大の勇気で！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.39,0:01:55.76,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}破れそうな　シルクノハート
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.86,0:01:59.40,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}キミに逢って気づいた　やっと
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.40,0:02:05.05,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}愛には不器用だったんだって
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.50,0:02:10.04,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}忘れかけた　恋の傷跡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.10,0:02:13.48,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}急に疼きだしたの　キュンと
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.64,0:02:17.07,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}いつかは私らしくスキと
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.15,0:02:23.04,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}言わなきゃ…今より弱くなっちゃうよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.05,0:00:58.63,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}My Silky Love　24小時中一直
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.63,0:01:02.17,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}My Silky Love　每當想起你的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.17,0:01:05.70,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}My Silky Love　心神不定的這份感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.70,0:01:09.71,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}My Silky Love　只是漸漸地漫溢出來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.11,0:01:13.59,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}明明說喜歡是如此簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.67,0:01:16.97,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}當你來到面前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.24,0:01:23.38,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}乖張的個性卻總妨礙著我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.35,0:01:27.78,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}平常的話可以逞強下去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.78,0:01:31.29,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}明明是這種性格
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.48,0:01:37.46,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}無論如何努力也無法打破壁障
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.57,0:01:41.19,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}希望你能覺察到 這份心情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.19,0:01:44.76,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}所以我 總是向你送去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.76,0:01:48.41,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}「最喜歡你了」的視線
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.51,0:01:52.16,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}用最大的勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.39,0:01:55.76,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}似乎快要扯破 絲絨般的心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.86,0:01:59.40,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}遇到你才終於明白
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.40,0:02:05.05,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}原來愛是這樣笨拙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.50,0:02:10.04,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}即將忘卻 戀愛的傷痛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.10,0:02:13.48,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}卻突然再次隱隱作疼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.64,0:02:17.07,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}如果有一天不說出自己的喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.15,0:02:23.04,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}將會變得比現在更加懦弱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-------正文------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.05,0:00:09.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在暫時無法接聽電話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.24,0:00:14.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請在聽到「嗶」聲之後留言
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.53,0:00:17.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  啊…櫛枝？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.56,0:00:19.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於今晚的平安夜的派對…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.41,0:00:21.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍兒你在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.52,0:00:24.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等會重新打來  派對一定要來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.69,0:00:23.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快來  把窗戶打開
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.04,0:00:26.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍兒  我說龍兒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.83,0:00:26.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會很開心的  就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.75,0:00:30.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好慢  你在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.32,0:00:33.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來  你才是在干什…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.41,0:00:34.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接住這個
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.53,0:00:40.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛那麼突然  真是兇暴…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.46,0:00:41.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別管那麼多  立刻打開它
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.80,0:00:42.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.74,0:00:44.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裏面的東西打開就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.88,0:00:47.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也準備一下30分鐘後就去你那裏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.67,0:00:48.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼等會見
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.14,0:00:50.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.18,0:00:53.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼什麼  發生什麼了YANSU
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.20,0:02:27.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.95,0:02:31.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.40,0:02:34.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好喔好喔  非常可愛哦大河妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.04,0:02:37.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小龍也來看看GANSU
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.38,0:02:38.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.94,0:02:43.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小龍也好帥YANSU
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.17,0:02:45.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  尺寸正合適嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.94,0:02:50.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這樣好嗎  借…借給我…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.57,0:02:52.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是借  是給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.19,0:02:54.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給…給我了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.68,0:02:57.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內襯上可是縫著「R.逢阪」的字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.55,0:02:58.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你老爸的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.52,0:03:01.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為尺寸不合所以一直扔在那裏所以沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.04,0:03:03.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那東西拿掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.63,0:03:07.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我穿他不要的  開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.04,0:03:09.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不穿的話就只好處理掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.52,0:03:16.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還真是適合幹這種細活呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.66,0:03:18.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你說拿掉的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.57,0:03:19.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,證據
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.47,0:03:21.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸚…鸚…鸚…秘
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.91,0:03:22.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.84,0:03:25.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個都能說了為什麼就說不了自己的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.82,0:03:26.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.67,0:03:30.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小魔女泰泰要給兩位施予魔法了YANSUGANSU哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.38,0:03:32.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔法？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.83,0:03:35.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能太鬧哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.26,0:03:37.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為派對開始的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.16,0:03:42.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就會散發出混合著大河妹妹氣味的清香了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.21,0:03:45.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  小龍就…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.14,0:03:46.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.50,0:03:50.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…  難道是老爸的？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.13,0:03:51.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的YANSU
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.56,0:03:53.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.74,0:04:00.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰泰離家出走的時候  就帶滿了值錢的東西逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.20,0:04:02.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說  這是爺爺的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.37,0:04:03.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯GANSU
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.42,0:04:06.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贓…贓…贓…贓…贓…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.74,0:04:08.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贓物？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.41,0:04:13.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看都要感冒了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.21,0:04:16.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}入場時請寫上班級和名字
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.18,0:04:18.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好多人  來了多少人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.72,0:04:21.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管來多少人重要的只有一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.67,0:04:25.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白嗎  你今晚可是有必須要做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.83,0:04:27.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.85,0:04:33.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦～小百合老師打扮了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.69,0:04:37.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不來派對原來是有約會了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.56,0:04:39.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是約會
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.35,0:04:44.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師今天要去參加專門為單身女性舉辦的房產購買講座
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.63,0:04:46.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,房產？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.70,0:04:49.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  老師要買公寓了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.73,0:04:53.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  為什麼特地是今天…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.25,0:04:54.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  那是因為啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.90,0:05:00.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平安夜有約會對象的女性都還未完全覺悟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.54,0:05:02.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要的東西突然出現的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.93,0:05:05.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就要馬上準備迎擊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.44,0:05:05.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.98,0:05:06.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.79,0:05:10.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  還要考慮選擇住房的事老師就先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.77,0:05:13.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家請注意不要出問題哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.47,0:05:14.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.20,0:05:15.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.09,0:05:17.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  你好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.70,0:05:19.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖誕樹修好了真是太好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.16,0:05:23.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成績也進步了  老師我好高興
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.75,0:05:25.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  老師
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.47,0:05:30.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想你們的努力一定會有回報的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.06,0:05:33.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  老師也一定找到想要的東西的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.69,0:05:35.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美妙的獨身生活等著你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.98,0:05:38.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…嗯  謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.26,0:05:41.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  各位
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.42,0:05:46.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天能來此參加失戀大明神企劃的聖誕派對
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.70,0:05:49.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真心地感謝大家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.80,0:05:51.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然發生了很多麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.76,0:05:55.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼樣  聖誕派對終於平安舉辦了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.79,0:05:53.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  北村那身打扮是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.34,0:05:55.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說  吐槽了就輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.99,0:06:00.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很感謝各位熱心的協助
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.07,0:06:04.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請在今天盡情地享受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.57,0:06:05.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.04,0:06:08.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.22,0:06:12.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慶祝今年的聖誕夜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.51,0:06:14.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Merry  Christmas
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.54,0:06:17.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Merry  Christmas！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.68,0:06:22.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢  雞腿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.91,0:06:26.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道哦  這個叫做火雞是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.82,0:06:28.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  是普通雞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.49,0:06:29.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家這樣說哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.24,0:06:33.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真美味  不愧是家養的火雞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.89,0:06:35.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.48,0:06:40.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈奈子  那邊有蛋糕哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.45,0:06:42.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧  哪裏哪裏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.11,0:06:43.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊的角落  去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.81,0:06:44.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.10,0:06:51.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿短褲的木原和穿清純連衣裙的奈奈子  好性感
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.22,0:06:54.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來  為什麼大家都打扮起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.30,0:06:57.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的好土  應該說是窮酸相了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.17,0:06:58.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  那邊的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.72,0:07:00.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要一邊四處張望一邊走路
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.11,0:07:02.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果子露都撒出來  地面會變得黏糊糊的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.45,0:07:03.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.18,0:07:05.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.13,0:07:06.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高須
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.76,0:07:09.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到處看不到你  你在這裏幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.59,0:07:13.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…因為手藝實在太差了  看著看著忍不住就…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.54,0:07:17.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來  原來你有這麼高級的西裝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.60,0:07:19.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好真好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.63,0:07:22.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你手上不都是雞油麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.26,0:07:24.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？  小高不知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.72,0:07:27.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是火雞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.20,0:07:30.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且是家養的火雞哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.50,0:07:29.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熏你好慢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.75,0:07:30.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.08,0:07:32.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.94,0:07:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.93,0:07:36.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.78,0:07:39.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還沒看到亞美  她來了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.40,0:07:41.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…嗯  大概
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.27,0:07:42.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好像瞄到過一眼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.89,0:07:45.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧  很性感嗎  如何性感了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.34,0:07:48.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在不在嗎  而且大河也…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.51,0:07:50.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大河嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.45,0:07:52.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  大河也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.52,0:07:55.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的啊  那傢伙去哪裏了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.22,0:07:55.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我果然還是亞美派呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.18,0:08:27.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞美和…大河？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.88,0:08:29.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔  好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.17,0:08:41.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那兩個傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.71,0:08:43.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底什麼時候做的這種練習…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.53,0:09:42.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  啊…櫛枝？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.51,0:09:44.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於今晚的平安夜的派對…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.38,0:09:46.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍兒你在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.36,0:09:48.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快來  把窗戶打開
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.84,0:09:51.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍兒  我說龍兒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.90,0:09:50.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等會重新打來  派對一定要來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.26,0:09:52.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會很開心的  就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.91,0:10:05.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真是太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.83,0:10:08.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞美和大河真是性感又可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.38,0:10:08.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.93,0:10:09.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.02,0:10:12.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說高須  你要做那個到什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.75,0:10:13.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.88,0:10:15.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的夢好像成真了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.98,0:10:19.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？  這和你做的夢完全不一樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.33,0:10:22.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  性感可愛什麼的差不多一樣了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.91,0:10:25.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦？  那我也來…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.39,0:10:27.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,性感可愛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.56,0:10:30.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,性感  好性感
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.03,0:10:31.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.03,0:10:35.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  你這個暴露裸體的變態
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.43,0:10:37.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說丸尾你在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.05,0:10:40.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  木原  我性感可愛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.33,0:10:41.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.65,0:10:43.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個似乎是性騷擾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.29,0:10:44.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,報仇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.67,0:10:49.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請給我水果雜燴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.67,0:10:49.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}註：一種飲料和水果的混合物，punch指五個、五種的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.40,0:10:50.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.10,0:10:52.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,川島
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.06,0:10:53.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來在這裏呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.65,0:10:55.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像順勢就變成這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.23,0:10:56.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶吶  歌怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.00,0:10:58.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常的好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.54,0:11:00.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候練習的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.31,0:11:04.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不保密的話就不能成為驚喜了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.57,0:11:05.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚇到了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.55,0:11:07.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  完全被蒙在鼓裏了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.90,0:11:10.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.08,0:11:11.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來  大河呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.95,0:11:13.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙也很努力的來著
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.70,0:11:16.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想給她份水果雜燴慰勞一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.26,0:11:17.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大河的話回去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.65,0:11:19.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.83,0:11:21.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.16,0:11:23.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎  沒注意到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.31,0:11:26.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是要去趟實乃梨家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.47,0:11:31.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了拉她來這裏  自己卻說要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.79,0:11:36.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是要準備迎接聖誕老人什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.55,0:11:39.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.24,0:11:40.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要回去…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.65,0:11:43.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道  大概有什麼不想看到的東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.46,0:11:46.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才忠告過你的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.29,0:11:47.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忠告？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.27,0:11:50.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這幼稚的家家酒  還是別再扮下去比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.06,0:11:53.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要演爸爸的角色呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.51,0:11:56.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.67,0:11:57.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…  川島
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.39,0:12:03.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊  根本沒在聽我說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.82,0:12:10.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天使大河大人為了大家幸福快樂的聖誕節
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.10,0:12:14.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經做好了脫一件兩件甚至全部脫光都可以的覺悟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.04,0:12:17.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣真的…好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.89,0:12:20.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要做個好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.70,0:12:23.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想成為某個幸福光景的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.62,0:12:28.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變成閃耀在聖誕之夜城鎮中的  一張幸福的笑臉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.96,0:12:33.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高須  也能給我一份水果雜燴嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.97,0:12:36.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡路里消耗過頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.91,0:12:37.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北村
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.96,0:12:40.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要出去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.04,0:12:43.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  高須
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.07,0:12:46.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.17,0:12:48.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能好啊
