Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.88,0:13:01.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的…真的是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.54,0:13:03.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.74,0:13:06.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍兒在等著小實來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.52,0:13:09.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還說「小實來之前絕對不回家」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.46,0:13:11.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「做好住在學校的覺悟了」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.43,0:13:15.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起小實
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.38,0:13:17.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  並不是討厭的對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.07,0:13:20.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是明白的  因為是朋友嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.31,0:13:22.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣才好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.04,0:13:26.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒來呢  聖誕老人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.72,0:13:30.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然只在聖誕節裏裝好孩子是沒用的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.77,0:13:35.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…本來就沒什麼聖誕老人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.83,0:13:39.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…今年也是一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.41,0:13:41.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來年也是一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.68,0:13:45.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這以後也是…一直
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.49,0:13:49.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直…無依無靠
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.32,0:13:53.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.69,0:13:59.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無依無靠？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.93,0:14:13.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.19,0:14:16.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從寢室那裏傳來的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.26,0:14:43.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖…聖誕老人？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.49,0:14:48.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.29,0:14:51.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.60,0:14:59.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的…是聖誕老人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.49,0:15:07.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.64,0:15:12.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.94,0:15:15.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  聖誕老人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.96,0:15:18.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是今年我家的聖誕樹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.03,0:15:25.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧對吧  太好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.48,0:15:27.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就想這個絕對是最棒的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.80,0:15:28.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.73,0:15:29.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.86,0:15:32.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖誕老人誇我的聖誕樹了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.58,0:15:46.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是現實呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.57,0:15:50.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害  夢想…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.74,0:15:53.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢想…成為現實了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.04,0:15:56.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.03,0:16:04.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.30,0:16:08.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.79,0:16:12.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  龍兒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.53,0:16:15.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別…別拿下來啊  笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.84,0:16:17.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還…還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.01,0:16:21.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我  你是在哪兒找到這種玩意兒的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.49,0:16:24.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向穿著這個的人借的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.45,0:16:27.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說你的西裝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.91,0:16:31.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以啊  跟穿這個的傢伙交換了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.47,0:16:33.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然待會兒會還回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.93,0:16:34.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當…當然
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.18,0:16:38.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然才要開始的時候就脫掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.07,0:16:40.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.50,0:16:41.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.42,0:16:43.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得都為你準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.42,0:16:45.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得終於能和小實見面了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.52,0:16:46.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋是什麼意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.14,0:16:50.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是說過要你相信天使大河大人了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.62,0:16:52.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小實應該在去派對的路上了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.03,0:16:54.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能已經到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.98,0:16:57.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  還來得及趕緊回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.04,0:16:59.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？  但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.50,0:17:02.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的裝扮都變成這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.76,0:17:04.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且也不想讓你一個人呆著
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.90,0:17:07.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.78,0:17:09.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的話已經沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.55,0:17:11.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝出來的聖誕老人和裝出來的好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.97,0:17:13.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常有趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.87,0:17:16.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  當然明天也很期待
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.84,0:17:19.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬一和小實進行順利的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.21,0:17:22.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天聖誕節就在高須家請你大吃一頓
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.16,0:17:24.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雞肉飯  牛肉飯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.97,0:17:28.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…因為有小鸚在  所以不能有雞肉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.58,0:17:30.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就只吃牛肉飯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.61,0:17:32.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  去吧  快點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.95,0:17:34.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但…但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.05,0:17:36.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果龍兒不在派對上的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.22,0:17:39.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就等於我對小實說謊了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.61,0:17:40.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點快點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.97,0:17:43.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  我說等一下啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.11,0:17:45.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為聖誕老人已經來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.11,0:17:47.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年我得做好孩子做到底
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.81,0:17:50.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以讓我做個好孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.15,0:17:57.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓小實去參加派對才是我給你真正的聖誕禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.23,0:18:00.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以拜託了  收下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.18,0:18:02.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大…河
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.50,0:18:06.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  快去  磨蹭狗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.98,0:18:10.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.37,0:18:20.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於走了終於走了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.07,0:18:24.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘記還給他了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.33,0:18:27.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.65,0:18:34.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.94,0:18:37.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.39,0:18:41.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.05,0:18:46.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在依靠著龍兒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.89,0:18:48.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依靠著龍兒的溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.57,0:18:52.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是已經結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.18,0:18:55.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小實一定會被龍兒所吸引
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.53,0:18:59.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍兒也是真心喜歡小實的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.07,0:19:03.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說  兩個人是相互喜歡的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.47,0:19:08.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後我也已經…不能再呆在龍兒身邊了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.67,0:19:11.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能走在龍兒的身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.00,0:19:16.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在龍兒身邊的…並不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.90,0:19:18.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.92,0:19:22.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…不要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.57,0:19:43.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍兒…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.67,0:19:47.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍兒！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.68,0:19:51.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍兒…龍兒…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.62,0:19:54.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍兒…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.07,0:19:59.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍兒…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.23,0:20:01.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍兒…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.18,0:20:19.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕透了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.31,0:20:21.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手機也沒帶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.03,0:20:25.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禮物也還放在西裝口袋裏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.70,0:20:28.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.49,0:20:30.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這真是只好熊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.81,0:20:32.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.07,0:20:35.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  哦…哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.78,0:20:39.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  櫛…櫛枝…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.13,0:20:39.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高須同學
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.63,0:20:43.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  讓我先說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.09,0:20:46.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個啊  還記得嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.65,0:20:49.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假的時候在亞美的別墅裏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.37,0:20:51.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夜晚我們兩個人不是說過了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.61,0:20:52.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.95,0:20:56.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,UFO什麼的  幽靈什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.24,0:20:57.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.93,0:20:59.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個呢  高須同學
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.68,0:21:02.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,UFO也好幽靈也好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.13,0:21:06.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想果然我還是不要看到的好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.21,0:21:09.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎還是不要看到的好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.75,0:21:13.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近想了很多  就開始這樣認為了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.53,0:21:17.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是想告訴高須同學這個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.93,0:21:19.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.64,0:21:20.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,櫛枝…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.28,0:21:23.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想說什麼就說了什麼很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.80,0:21:26.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,櫛枝就這樣回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.05,0:21:32.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？  不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.67,0:21:34.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說…啥來著
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.62,0:21:38.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是…  失…戀？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.52,0:23:27.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被櫛枝甩了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.28,0:23:28.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是這樣閉上眼就…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.50,0:23:30.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高須同學  !@#$%^
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.93,0:23:32.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經聽到了跟平常一樣開朗的聲音了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.77,0:23:34.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  爆了
